Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:01.31,Default,An EF-4 tornado tore through
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.85,0:00:04.01,Default,Enid, Oklahoma, and the shocking
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.01,0:00:04.94,Default,part is that no one
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.17,0:00:06.33,Default,died. This was not a
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.41,0:00:06.72,Default,near miss.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.11,0:00:08.42,Default,The storm packed one hundred
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.96,0:00:10.97,Default,seventy to one hundred seventy
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.97,0:00:12.13,Default,five mile per hour winds
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.52,0:00:13.83,Default,and carved a violent path
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.14,0:00:15.68,Default,straight through town.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.68,0:00:16.69,Default,It stayed on the ground
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.15,0:00:19.24,Default,for about nine miles, stretched
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.24,0:00:21.40,Default,roughly five hundred yards wide,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.40,0:00:23.41,Default,and damaged around forty homes
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.41,0:00:24.26,Default,in and around Enid.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.65,0:00:27.28,Default,Emergency crews searched homes, pulled
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.28,0:00:29.75,Default,trapped residents out, and officials
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.75,0:00:31.14,Default,said the city somehow escaped
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.68,0:00:33.31,Default,with only minor injuries
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.31,0:00:35.16,Default,instead of mass casualties.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.16,0:00:36.17,Default,That is why this story
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.55,0:00:38.87,Default,matters. Usually when damage looks
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.87,0:00:40.88,Default,this severe, there are deaths.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.88,0:00:42.58,Default,Enid got extremely lucky.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.58,0:00:43.66,Default,The lesson is not that
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.97,0:00:45.29,Default,the storm was weaker than
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.59,0:00:45.75,Default,it looked.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.29,0:00:48.38,Default,The lesson is that preparation,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.38,0:00:50.39,Default,shelter, and response made the
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.39,0:00:52.40,Default,difference when the worst case
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.40,0:00:53.55,Default,almost happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.55,0:00:55.56,Default,Preparation is boring right up
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.56,0:00:56.96,Default,until it saves a town.
